♡First prize $5000💸💸
♡Second prize $3000
♡third prize $1000

♡Choose from any of our meal plans: Allergy Friendly, Vegan, Standard, Vegetarian or Gluten Free. Also enjoy full access to our Smoothie Bar, Family Meals and Healthy Treats

♡Top the leaderboard and win a $1k fitness prize pack full of my go to fitness accessories

♡Full access to the app during the challenge, add glute activations, hiits or ab sessions depending on your personal goals.

♡Weekly giveaways & exclusive discounts with brands like Seed & Sprout, Saski Collection, New Balance etc

♡Support 7 days a week with the Tammy Fit team.
